...how to help a guy loosen up
and have a good time.

17:59.453 --> 18:03.164
Although, truth be told,
my groin's a little worse for wear.

18:04.249 --> 18:05.792
Ow!

18:09.213 --> 18:11.172
-Why'd you do that?
-To send a message.

18:11.340 --> 18:13.591
She is not for you.

18:14.259 --> 18:16.177
-What?
-Not for you.

18:27.064 --> 18:28.856
Good morning, handsome.

18:29.858 --> 18:31.776
Morning, Mom.

18:34.571 --> 18:36.572
It's me.

18:38.534 --> 18:41.369
Yes, it is.
And you're so pretty in the morning.

18:43.372 --> 18:45.164
Your mom and I made you breakfast.

18:45.332 --> 18:48.751
Oh, wow, heh,
so you guys are getting along?

18:48.919 --> 18:50.545
Yeah, I guess.

18:50.712 --> 18:54.465
We're very different people, Howard,
so communication's a little tricky.

18:54.633 --> 18:56.843
MRS. WOLOWITZ:
Does he like the pancakes?

18:57.010 --> 18:59.053
He didn't try them yet!

19:02.391 --> 19:05.351
-Is there any butter? Heh.
-It's butter-flavored syrup.

19:05.519 --> 19:07.019
MRS. WOLOWITZ:
So? What's the word?

19:07.187 --> 19:09.147
He wants butter!

19:10.816 --> 19:12.859
MRS. WOLOWITZ:
It's butter-flavored syrup!

19:13.026 --> 19:15.695
I just told him that!

19:21.618 --> 19:22.869
I don't need any butter.

19:23.036 --> 19:26.080
If you want butter, I'll get you butter.

19:30.210 --> 19:33.212
Well, I guess I'll cut these by myself.

20:02.451 --> 20:04.452
[English - US - SDH]
